OL,3,CCraig Bellamy accepts cheering against
OL,4,CEngland was wrong
OL,6,FCraig Bellamy has addressed bullying
OL,7,Fand xenophobic behaviour allegations
OL,8,Fmade against him during his time as an
OL,9,Facademy coach and says he was wrong to
OL,10,Fcheer against England in front of
OL,11,Fyoung English footballers.
OL,13,FThe new Wales manager stepped down
OL,14,Ffrom his position as Cardiff Under-18s
OL,15,Fcoach in January 2019 as the Sky Bet
OL,16,FChampionship club conducted claims
OL,17,Fagainst him and others.
