OL,3,CCraig Bellamy accepts cheering against
OL,4,CEngland was wrong
OL,6,FThe following October, Cardiff said
OL,7,Ftheir academy players had faced an
OL,8,F"unacceptable coaching environment" at
OL,9,Fthe club.
OL,11,FAs well as supporting England's
OL,12,Fopponents in front of young English
OL,13,Fplayers, Bellamy was said to have
OL,14,Fturned the sound down on the
OL,15,Ftelevision when God Save The Queen was
OL,16,Fplaying before England's 2018 World
OL,17,FCup semi-final with Croatia and also
OL,18,Fshown his contempt for Bristol City.
