OL,3,CCraig Bellamy accepts cheering against
OL,4,CEngland was wrong
OL,6,FBellamy, who denied and disputed the
OL,7,Fallegations and was not the subject of
OL,8,Fany disciplinary proceedings,
OL,9,Fapologised for any offence he caused
OL,10,Fand subsequently rebuilt his coaching
OL,11,Fcareer by assisting Vincent Kompany at
OL,12,FAnderlecht and Burnley.
OL,14,FThe 45-year-old, who won 78 Wales caps
OL,15,Fand played for Liverpool, Manchester
OL,16,FCity and Newcastle, says he did not
OL,17,Fappreciate how his behaviour could
OL,18,Fimpact young players in the Cardiff
OL,19,Facademy.
