OL,3,CCraig Bellamy accepts cheering against
OL,4,CEngland was wrong
OL,6,FHe spent over two years in Belgium
OL,7,Fbefore being reunited with Kompany at
OL,8,FBurnley, during which time the Clarets
OL,9,Fwon the Championship title with 101
OL,10,Fpoints and then suffered Premier
OL,11,FLeague relegation.
OL,13,FBellamy said: "I went to Anderlecht
OL,14,Fand had an opportunity again to work
OL,15,Fwith under-18s.
OL,17,F"But the amount of relationships I
OL,18,Fstill have with a lot of players from
OL,19,Fthose (Cardiff) moments is hugely
OL,20,Fimportant to me as well.
