OL,3,CCraig Bellamy accepts cheering against
OL,4,CEngland was wrong
OL,6,F"The message for every youth coach who
OL,7,Fgoes into youth coaching is, 'please,
OL,8,Fbe mindful. Please. Really do your
OL,9,Fhomework and the levels you're going
OL,10,Finto and what you allow'.
OL,12,F"I wasn't dealing with 12, 13 or 14
OL,13,Fyear-olds. These were 17, 18-year-
OL,14,Folds. If you're in school, then
OL,15,Fobviously you don't swear.
OL,17,F"I thought, after school, maybe, you
OL,18,Fknow, in that environment, I could
OL,19,Fturn a blind eye to it. But you can't
OL,20,Fdo that."
